  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>You've been kidnapped by a deranged clown and forced into a deadly game. In a decaying execution chamber, the only way to survive is to defeat all your opponents...</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Blackjack Roulette\" is a roguelike card game that combines blackjack with Russian roulette. Build a unique deck of trump cards to face eight twisted opponents, or outsmart real players in intense 1v1 duels. Every hand is a life-or-death gamble. Will you survive to face the Joker?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/74eab721c020000111a2bfdffa8b1aba.avif?t=1774007989\" width=750 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/5c68db9d5d03c810b6bb421efc9bc1e8.poster.avif?t=1774007989\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/5c68db9d5d03c810b6bb421efc9bc1e8.webm?t=1774007989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/5c68db9d5d03c810b6bb421efc9bc1e8.mp4?t=1774007989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in a twisted version of the classic 21-point duel. The loser must pick up a revolver and pull the trigger...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/5d631d7a4c6ddb4b0b941b4936b8454d.avif?t=1774007989\" width=750 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/bee46d6fb49a27f9d033d0552bdda64c.poster.avif?t=1774007989\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/bee46d6fb49a27f9d033d0552bdda64c.webm?t=1774007989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/bee46d6fb49a27f9d033d0552bdda64c.mp4?t=1774007989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Draw and play special cards that can completely turn the tables—force your opponent to draw, peek at hidden cards, or even swap out bullets in the gun. Outsmart your enemies and drive them to their doom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/1c9f61322dda01bc63ccf0381851ad92.avif?t=1774007989\" width=750 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/cc24ac743b46a55495f8a07531229e69.poster.avif?t=1774007989\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/cc24ac743b46a55495f8a07531229e69.webm?t=1774007989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/cc24ac743b46a55495f8a07531229e69.mp4?t=1774007989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the short-tempered \"Punk-ass Thug\" to the unpredictable \"Bankrupt Blowhard,\" you must defeat 8 brutal opponents until you face the ultimate boss, the deranged Clown, in your bid for survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you outwit death, or become its next victim?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/676ca90c5bbc5869b2ecc75c9fa62794.avif?t=1774007989\" width=750 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/8e1a0b2de4f3a05b095383014a1a69a2.poster.avif?t=1774007989\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/8e1a0b2de4f3a05b095383014a1a69a2.webm?t=1774007989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4218600/extras/8e1a0b2de4f3a05b095383014a1a69a2.mp4?t=1774007989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your skills against real players in intense 1v1 online duels. Only the sharpest minds will survive and emerge victorious.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>This is not just a game; it's a survival experiment.</strong></h2>",
